Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.64,0:00:06.94,main,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,The time is upon us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.69,0:00:12.49,main,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,Our long-held wish shall be fulfilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.54,0:00:29.21,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for bringing us this far, Fitoria-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:32.51,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,And for the new wagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.88,0:00:36.23,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Filo really loves pulling one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.10,0:00:47.27,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,It's mine now, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.02,0:00:51.03,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.94,0:00:53.79,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Fitoria...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.53,0:00:56.57,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Is another hero nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.16,0:00:59.87,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I sense one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.16,0:01:01.51,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.51,0:01:02.96,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Shield Hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.20,0:01:06.12,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.21,0:01:10.34,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,And keep your promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.88,0:01:14.17,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll do what I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.45,0:01:41.28,sign_3370_33_The_Rising_of_th,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,1)}The Rising of the Shield Hero
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.48,0:03:01.20,sign_5367_37_Lullaby_at_Dawn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(486,768)}A Conspiracy Linked
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:24.60,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,If only we could get past that wall, \Nwe could cross the border.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:27.89,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Any other routes we could take, Raphtalia-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:33.48,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Taking a detour would \Ncost us a few more days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.10,0:03:38.78,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Fitoria-san said there was \Nanother hero nearby, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:41.74,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,It might be better to take a detour anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:44.78,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,What will we do, Naofumi-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.08,0:03:48.70,flashback,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really try to make up with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:53.29,flashback,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't tell them they're wrong, \Nyou're basically admitting your guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.63,0:03:56.71,flashback,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Shield Hero... keep your promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:01.09,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We'll head down to the checkpoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:04.68,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,If it's Itsuki or Ren there, we'll talk \Nto them and have them let us through.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.14,0:04:08.22,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,And what if they refuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:10.72,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll force our way through.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.31,0:04:12.69,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.02,0:04:16.02,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:16.81,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.23,0:04:21.19,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd try to stop me because \Nit could make my reputation worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:27.28,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,There are guys like Idol who want to kill you, even if they have to summon a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:29.70,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the time to be \Nworrying about appearances.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:31.41,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,True that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.12,0:04:35.25,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready. We're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.25,0:04:36.92,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:43.69,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.48,0:04:57.36,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:05:00.11,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I see the spear guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:05.11,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I get the guy least likely \Nto hear me out, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:06.78,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:08.48,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late to turn back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:10.28,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:17.88,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Motoyasu, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:20.38,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We're not here to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:23.84,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,All we ask is that you let us through.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:26.80,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.34,0:05:28.22,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:30.93,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all you have to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:33.39,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Devil of the Shield?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:39.24,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:42.69,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Who attacks someone without \Neven listening to them first?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.69,0:05:48.11,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,You're still using your brainwashing shield \Nto enslave Filo and Raphtalia-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:50.15,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,How despicable!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.15,0:05:51.66,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,That shield doesn't exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.66,0:05:54.49,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to talk your way out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:58.92,flashback,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Heroes are supposed to work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.63,0:06:02.63,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hear me out, Motoyasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:04.80,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:06.13,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hell, even last time—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:08.63,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I was summoned to this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.55,0:06:12.64,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,to stop you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:16.39,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Meteor Thrust!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:34.49,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,You still won't go down?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.49,0:06:36.91,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,You're stubborn if nothing else,\Nyou damned devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:38.66,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:43.37,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama, you can't talk \Nanything out when he's like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.88,0:06:45.13,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,This guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:47.05,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:50.76,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Motoyasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:53.60,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.60,0:06:56.47,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because I ran away last time? \NDid it piss you off that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.47,0:06:58.98,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,To you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:03.31,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Were Ren and Itsuki that \Ninsignificant to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:08.32,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,I finally understand that \Nyou really are a devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:09.65,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.65,0:07:12.74,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,You tricked us by saying \Nwe were on the same team
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:15.33,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,as heroes, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:17.08,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.33,0:07:20.18,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,You are the scum of the earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.95,0:07:26.55,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,I will make you pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.46,0:07:30.05,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what did I even do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:31.00,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Search your feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.00,0:07:31.88,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,You'll know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:34.64,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,He's seriously trying to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.18,0:07:38.39,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:43.19,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you pay for \Nkilling Itsuki and Ren!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:49.74,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I killed them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:51.62,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.62,0:07:54.53,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to play dumb, you accursed devil?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.95,0:08:01.96,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,You should know why I'm so angry and hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:04.63,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,You killed them both!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:07.09,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:10.01,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:12.52,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,The heroes of the Bow and Sword were killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:16.72,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,You used your brainwashing \Nshield on Princess Melty, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.72,0:08:18.39,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,You filthy swine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:20.48,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Again, I have no such thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:23.56,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,If Motoyasu is telling the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:27.86,flashback,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,If even one Cardinal Hero is \Nmissing when a Wave hits,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.86,0:08:30.65,flashback,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,fighting it off will be \Nexponentially more difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:33.61,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, Motoyasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:37.62,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't killed Ren or Itsuki!\N I have no need to!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:38.58,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:41.62,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see their bodies for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:44.12,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:45.62,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Then it may be a lie—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.62,0:08:49.00,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,It's reliable information \Nfrom an agent of the Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:52.97,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,They said the Devil of the Shield unleashed \Na monster sealed in the center of town
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:57.03,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,and killed Itsuki-sama and Ren-sama \Nwhile they were distracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:08:59.23,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.23,0:09:02.52,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Motoyasu-sama, be wary of \Nhis brainwashing shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.76,0:09:05.69,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let the devil sway you with his words.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.69,0:09:07.48,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.86,0:09:09.69,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be fooled!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:12.40,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she always like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.45,0:09:15.70,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Mel-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.70,0:09:17.95,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Sister, you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:20.66,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Did you kill Ren and Itsuki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:23.70,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Now, it is time to battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:33.96,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.96,0:09:35.67,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,A Lightning Cage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:39.85,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. An item that seals caster and target
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:42.18,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,in an impregnable lightning prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.18,0:09:43.89,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.89,0:09:45.81,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,I will avenge their deaths!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:48.85,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down and think this through, Motoyasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:52.08,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to believe something \Nwithout confirming it for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.30,0:09:56.29,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in my trustworthy friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.59,0:09:58.24,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,What a clown!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:10:00.78,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,He's dancing in the palm of her hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:02.16,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.58,0:10:10.84,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Shield Prison!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.13,0:10:19.80,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Our levels are too far apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:21.05,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Filo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.05,0:10:23.31,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:24.85,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:28.76,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,As source of thy power and the \Nnext queen, I order thee.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:31.48,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,That's one haughty incantation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.74,0:10:37.24,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Decipher the laws of creation and \Ndrench my targets in a rain of flame!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:40.20,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Zweit Fire Squall!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:48.46,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Nullify the flames raining \Ndown upon my targets!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:52.17,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Anti-Zweit Fire Squall!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:54.67,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:56.63,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You ready, Filo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:57.50,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:04.67,main,Adv,0000,0000,0000,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:06.80,main,Adv,0000,0000,0000,,Zweit Air Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:26.37,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.37,0:11:29.41,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,That's the move she picked up in \Nthe duel with Fitoria-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.41,0:11:31.08,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,She's already making good use of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:33.38,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, Filo-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:38.09,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,I must fight for Ren and Itsuki, \Neven if it means hurting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:52.02,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Meteor Thrust!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.52,0:11:58.00,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.28,0:11:59.61,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Chaos Spear!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:03.49,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Myne! Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:05.20,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Zweit Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:07.24,main,Adv,0000,0000,0000,,Zweit Air Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.21,0:12:15.58,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Behold this combo skill involving \Nfire, wind, and my spear!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:19.76,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Air-Burst Flare Lance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:28.85,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:31.31,main,Adv,0000,0000,0000,,Zweit Air Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:33.98,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Zweit Aqua Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:38.89,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Melty...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:40.94,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:46.07,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Is this... a combo skill?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:50.54,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You saw their attack just now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.54,0:12:51.58,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.58,0:12:52.96,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.70,0:12:57.16,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,If you continue to side with him, \NI won't show you any mercy, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.96,0:13:00.71,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,As source of thy power, I order thee.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.71,0:13:03.97,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Decipher the laws of nature \Nand conceal my target.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:06.18,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,First Hiding!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:08.26,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hiding Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:15.77,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Change Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.94,0:13:22.19,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Motoyasu-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:30.20,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,He drained my SP?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:32.42,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think I am?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.66,0:13:35.79,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need to use any skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:36.75,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Filo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.17,0:13:38.63,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,High Quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.37,0:13:44.13,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Motoyasu-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.13,0:13:45.35,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,You're wide open.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.14,0:13:50.39,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,You will not get in Naofumi-sama's way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.18,0:13:55.38,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,A damned demi-human thinks she can \Nstrike me not once, but twice?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:56.86,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.86,0:14:01.27,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,How could you force Filo-chan and \NRaphtalia-chan to attack others for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:03.07,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You still don't get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:03.95,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.95,0:14:05.82,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Filo! Melty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.32,0:14:09.16,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,As source of thy power, we order thee!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:13.66,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Decipher the laws of nature and \Nbring forth a raging wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:16.91,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Bring forth a pelting rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.93,0:14:20.29,main,Bo,0000,0000,0000,,And produce a storm that \Nblows our targets away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:22.75,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Typhoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:22.75,top,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Typhoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.81,0:14:32.68,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,That was great, Filo-chan! \NWe were in perfect sync!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:33.81,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.23,0:14:40.65,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:44.48,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so strong when \Nyou haven't upgraded classes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:47.74,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Is this because of the \Nbrainwashing shield, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.74,0:14:50.86,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,While you were having fun playing superhero,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.86,0:14:54.46,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,we were out here fighting \Nand acquiring skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.46,0:14:55.70,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.70,0:14:58.67,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,You think I'll believe \Nthat trite explanation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.93,0:15:00.62,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.75,0:15:05.58,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We did what we had to do, \Nno matter how trite or trivial.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.58,0:15:07.55,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why you lost to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:12.14,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Give it a rest, Motoyasu. Hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.22,0:15:14.56,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:19.64,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I must avenge Itsuki and Ren.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.64,0:15:23.23,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,If I give in here, Princess Melty, \NRaphtalia-chan, and Filo-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:27.69,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,will never be freed from \Nthe Devil of the Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.69,0:15:30.15,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,I will never accept that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.15,0:15:33.91,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm the Spear Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.23,0:15:36.86,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,That's my Motoyasu-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.24,0:15:42.50,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Bring me the Devil of the Shield's \Nhead and my dear Melty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.25,0:15:50.26,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,How can I talk this thickheaded buffoon\Ndown when he's got a hero complex?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:52.05,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Filo-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.64,0:15:55.77,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,This is odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:15:58.97,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,All those soldiers are gone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.78,0:16:14.57,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Filo, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:16.46,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,The shield, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.46,0:16:18.62,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Bring out that dark shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:22.46,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,And place a bunch of stuff above us! \NOr else we're done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:23.42,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:25.78,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.97,0:16:30.80,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Shield Prison!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.39,0:16:35.63,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,More!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.22,0:16:37.85,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Up top, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:39.60,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Air Strike Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.18,0:16:42.10,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Second Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.40,0:16:46.77,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,What are you playing at?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:48.48,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:49.94,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.97,0:17:59.18,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:01.72,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Are Filo and Melty okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.14,0:18:03.27,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,We're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:04.85,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:08.68,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,What just happened, Myne?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:11.41,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That power...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.27,0:18:13.61,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:23.87,main,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,My, how wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:29.75,main,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,You take the high-class multi-caster \Nritual magic, Judgment,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.28,0:18:32.63,main,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,head-on and remain standing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:37.68,main,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,I'd expect nothing less from the Shield Devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:41.55,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,The Pope?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:45.72,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You're that guy from the \Ncapital's cathedral!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:48.81,main,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You remember who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.81,0:18:52.23,main,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,Then you must be aware of your sin as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.23,0:18:53.69,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,My sin?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.02,0:19:00.45,main,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,You not only showed no gratitude for \Nthe holy water God bestowed upon you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:04.95,main,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,but also deceived the people and led \Nthem to turn against the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.95,0:19:06.16,main,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,Hence,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.50,0:19:12.29,main,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,I shall purify you all in the name of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:15.13,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Pope Balmus!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:17.63,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Do you realize what you have just done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:22.09,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,You nearly killed the Spear Hero\N and the next queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:27.56,main,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,The Spear Hero's party and the next queen \Nwere killed by the Devil of the Shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:30.06,main,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,Or, well, that's how the script goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:34.11,main,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you are \Nall walking corpses.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.11,0:19:35.40,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:38.04,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Myne, what the hell is he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:42.74,main,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,And if walking corpses become\Nreal corpses,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:45.28,main,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,that just means all is right in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:49.01,main,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,It is all as God desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.01,0:19:50.90,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:53.38,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,That's some messed-up logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.88,0:19:55.42,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Reminds me of a certain someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.05,0:19:58.55,main,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you may rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:20:02.13,main,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,We have already planned a system of \Ngovernment to take the royal family's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.13,0:20:02.96,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:05.05,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.48,0:20:09.13,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,No one but us can rule this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.13,0:20:12.85,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Royalty that abuse their power \Nand mistreat the Church,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.85,0:20:15.89,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,apostles of God Himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.19,0:20:18.90,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Neither the country nor its people \Nneed such blasphemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.90,0:20:23.10,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,If anything, you are a pestilence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:26.20,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,And the same goes for you heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:32.71,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,We worship the ones who save the \Npeople and the world from the Waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.71,0:20:33.79,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.17,0:20:38.13,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,The Spear Hero released a sealed \Nmonster upon the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:40.75,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,the Sword Hero caused an epidemic,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.22,0:20:44.34,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,and the Bow Hero tried to \Nconceal his standing and hide from his duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.59,0:20:51.97,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Heroes who cause harm across the country and \Ndamage the people's belief are nothing but fakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.97,0:20:56.90,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,I... I did it because I thought \Nit would help the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.23,0:20:59.19,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Ren and Itsuki were trying to help, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.19,0:21:01.40,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,And you call us fakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.15,0:21:05.11,main,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,Your foolishness speaks volumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.11,0:21:10.12,main,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,As did theirs, when they started \Ninvestigating something beyond them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:11.29,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Investigating?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.29,0:21:15.62,main,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,That is why God's Judgment fell upon them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.08,0:21:17.96,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,God's Judgment?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.96,0:21:22.46,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a second! Didn't Naofumi kill them?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.24,0:21:30.62,main,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,You've put on quite the \Namusing farce, but enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.60,0:21:37.72,main,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,For the false Spear Hero
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.72,0:21:39.40,main,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,and for the Devil of the Shield,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.40,0:21:43.02,main,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,clinging so desperately \Nto life like a cockroach,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.02,0:21:45.40,main,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,let there be the purification of Holy Judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.05,0:21:48.36,main,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.45,0:21:52.33,main,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,For this country, righteous order!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.43,0:21:58.00,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out, Naofumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.40,0:21:59.80,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,That sword is...
